{"tid":1067152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] Multiple people hurt in Dutch tram shooting incident","createTime":"2019-03-18T10:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T11:14:16.000Z","uid":52215,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ed2aaa8c22d70fcc3599da3459e06131e1aab93f","tid":1067152,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T10:38:35.000Z","msg":"Utrecht: Multiple people hurt in Dutch tram shooting incident<br />\nBy Rosanne Roobeek<br />\nUpdated 3月 18, 2019<br />\n(CNN) - Multiple people have been injured in a shooting in the Dutch town of Utrecht, police say.<br />\nThe incident unfolded on or near a tram, according to Joost Lanshage, spokesman for the police in central Holland. <br />\nLocal police confirmed on Twitter that the incident took place at the 24th of October Square, which has been closed off. <br />\nThe shooting, which was reported at 10:45 a.m. (5:45 a.m ET), is now over -- however the police operation is ongoing, Lanshage added.<br />\nEmergency responders are attending the scene. <br />\nThis story is developing -- More details to come.<br />\nTM &amp; &copy; 2019 Turner Broadcasting System, Inc.<br />\nA WarnerMedia Company.<br />\nAll Rights Reserved."},{"pid":"060e001acd9695a069b367e83c6148a94c083077","tid":1067152,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T10:39:04.000Z","msg":"ww4<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f8c492ebf4dc7e41606c22fb0782524de28cdd","tid":1067152,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T10:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf5900cbc5c036f971936567f244460a9d6690c","tid":1067152,"uid":98887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T10:39:25.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" clas